description: Demolition of existing buildings and redevelopment of the site to provide 5 storey mixed use scheme comprising 548.4 sqm of office floor space (Use Class B1) at ground floor level and 60 residential units (Use Class C3) at first to fourth floor levels, with associated amenity space, 61 car parking spaces and cycle parking, refuse and recycling storage facilities, and landscaping provision.
